<subSubSection id="C30B657FFFB8540EFF548624FBF4E8F2" box="[199,1065,880,903]" pageId="3" pageNumber="587" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BAE36F4FFB8540EFF548624FBF4E8F2" blockId="3.[151,1436,151,972]" box="[199,1065,880,903]" pageId="3" pageNumber="587">
<emphasis id="B965EAE6FFB8540EFF548624FE9AE8F2" bold="true" box="[199,327,880,903]" pageId="3" pageNumber="587">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet refers to the black markings on head and thorax.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C30B657FFFB8540EFF5486C6FAB9E8B9" pageId="3" pageNumber="587" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BAE36F4FFB8540EFF5486C6FAB9E8B9" blockId="3.[151,1436,151,972]" pageId="3" pageNumber="587">
<emphasis id="B965EAE6FFB8540EFF5486C6FEE8E8DC" bold="true" box="[199,309,914,937]" pageId="3" pageNumber="587">Remarks.</emphasis>
